               <p>WILLIAM STOW. I am her husband; I will take her back, and not upbraid her with what is past - we will live happily together. I will give security for my good conduct to her; we merely parted on account of difficulties - I have nothing to say against her, but poverty came in, and we had words.</p>
               <p>Prisoner. I will go back to him, and be an affectionate good <rs id="t18320906-132-deflabel751" type="occupation">wife</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320906-132-defend1135 t18320906-132-deflabel751"></join>.</p>
